# System Health

!!! info "System Health Overview"
    This page lists instruments currently in a degraded state (**Warning** or **Offline**) and why.

{% if issues %}

<div class="aic-grid aic-grid--compact">
  {% for inst in issues %}
  <div class="aic-card" aria-label="Status for {{ inst.display_name }}">
    <div class="aic-card__body">
      <div class="aic-card__title">{{ inst.display_name }}</div>
      <div class="aic-card__meta">{{ inst.manufacturer }}{% if inst.model %} · {{ inst.model }}{% endif %}</div>

      <div class="aic-statusline">
        <span class="aic-badge aic-badge--{{ inst.status.color }}">{{ inst.status.badge }}</span>
        <span class="aic-muted">{{ inst.status.reason }}</span>
      </div>

      <div class="aic-kv">
        <div><span class="aic-muted">Last QC</span><br>{{ inst.status.last_qc_date or '—' }}</div>
        <div><span class="aic-muted">Last Maintenance</span><br>{{ inst.status.last_maint_date or '—' }}</div>
      </div>

      <div class="aic-actions">
        <a href="instruments/{{ inst.id }}/index.md" class="md-button md-button--small">Overview</a>
        <a href="instruments/{{ inst.id }}/history.md" class="md-button md-button--primary md-button--small">View History</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

{% else %}

!!! success "No Active Issues"
    All instruments are currently healthy.

{% endif %}
